    <h2>Did You Know?</h2>
    
        <div id="dyk-trademark" class="see-more inline canwrap">

                <h4 class="inline">Trademark:</h4>
Funny satirical way of narrating the stories on the education system or the system in general with a subtle message encouraging idealism and humanism                    <span class="see-more inline">
                        <a href="/name/nm0386246/bio?ref_=nm_dyk_tm_sm#trademark"
>See more</a>
                    </span>
                    &raquo;
        </div>
    
            <hr/>
        <div id="dyk-nickname" class="see-more inline canwrap">
            <h4 class="inline">Nickname:</h4>
            Raju
        </div>
            <hr/>
        <div id="dyk-star-sign" class="see-more inline canwrap">
            <h4 class="inline">Star Sign:</h4>
            <a href="/starsign/scorpio?ref_=nm_dyk_sign"
>Scorpio</a>
        </div>
